{"tid":1426351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]兄弟皮藝公開支持警察同政府，熱愛祖國！","createTime":"2019-08-07T01:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:20:29.000Z","uid":167441,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"675abd19ccfd23b2514d0f99ef22dceee156112b","tid":1426351,"uid":167441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"事源經朋友分享 係一個微信群組入面 <br />\n發現有一班內地人搜集左啲資料<br />\n批評兄弟皮藝政治立場<br />\n之後再上兄弟皮藝既淘寶店 <br />\n發現出左一張 支持警察同政府等字句既圖片<br />\n但今日起身已經發現成間淘寶店唔見左<br />\n之前都有睇開兄弟皮藝 既FACEBOOK <br />\n發現佢既立場有啲奇怪 之前佢經常出POST <br />\n擺工,黑色case airpods等等 <br />\n夠竟佢係咩立場?? 我睇唔透阿<br />\n等睇老闆解釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VufzZ0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVufzZ0k.jpg&h=fbc85245&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">兄弟皮藝淘寶店(今日淘寶店突然消失)</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rr6fKr0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRr6fKr0.jpg&h=37c4f9c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">內地網民既意見</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2p9hdkk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2p9hdkk.jpg&h=4dde3433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">內地網民既資料</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qu728TG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQu728TG.jpg&h=2f1465b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">兄弟皮藝淘寶店回應</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAneZ0m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAneZ0m.jpg&h=46b96249&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">兄弟皮藝之前既post, 黑色case airpods</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兄弟皮藝係香港其中一間最大皮革既Distributor<br />\n供應俾唔同local handmade workshop (但以我所知好多workshop 都係黃) <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎大家去Facebook或親臨店鋪 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>查詢皮革資料</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BrothersLeathercraft/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBrothersLeathercraft%2F&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apFtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=bcf216eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BrothersLeathercraft/</a></span><br />\n香港深水埗大南街207-209號地鋪</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a8dedabc4cc852f8003b9409b01d9056a51b17e","tid":1426351,"uid":167441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:04:59.000Z","msg":"想睇老闆回應"},{"pid":"c5efffedb59776d932d37bbb70379f1f2edf1d7f","tid":1426351,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da69dff21dc0948ef4c3a960ed665dc66c11d38d","tid":1426351,"uid":167441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5efffedb59776d932d37bbb70379f1f2edf1d7f","tid":1426351,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45034815bb956c3bfcebfc3643614c7473fa529b","tid":1426351,"uid":167441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"